</ImageGalleryImage>
<ImageGalleryImage alt="IBM Design" title="IBM Design" col={4}>

![不同SMX的并行](/b.png)

</ImageGalleryImage>

</ImageGallery>

### GPU 和 CPU 处理问题的编码方式异同

<ImageGallery>
<ImageGalleryImage alt="IBM Design" title="IBM Design" col={4}>

![问题](/c.png)

</ImageGalleryImage>
<ImageGalleryImage alt="IBM Design" title="IBM Design" col={4}>

